{"title":"Paper. DROGAS INMUNOSUPRESORAS-2025-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Bioestadística/Paper. DROGAS INMUNOSUPRESORAS-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"DROGAS\\NINMUNOSUPRESORAS","guid":"9VGDzwqrPm8hXb3Jw5iKLA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## INTRODUCCIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Concepto: Mecanismos biológicos → respuesta de rechazo en trasplante","guid":"zAHJdKa8EljUr-6NxFfxMg","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Historia: Desde los 60s, pruebas de productos/radiaciones","guid":"eyICqj9wpR3HAdb810cuHw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- Distinción:","guid":"YGgQnimhcqLCJ6CqaDik4g","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"- Inducción: Aceptación inicial del injerto","guid":"i45pEqv6H_eW8xMDmJ12-g","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"- Mantención: Supresión de rechazo a largo plazo","guid":"BOVBt45d47FX1Gq9VV9Lbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"- Investigación\\NInmunológica:","guid":"Dfkdrm96bQab8ic-CwRV9w","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"- Necesidad de anular respuesta efectora (CPA, LT citotóxicos, LB)","guid":"BhoGbqaBEPNYjRMsBDgwSw","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"- Reconocimiento de respuesta de tolerancia (estimulable in vivo)","guid":"Zx8PiY5sOXKXuOgvktJmGQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"## INDUCCIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- Contexto:","guid":"Bx1Fj6ZgMwCAv1W1aG9b0A","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"- ~10% LT naive entrenados vs aloantígenos","guid":"oNoVzuoY6sIFVYlOga_4fA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"- LT y LB efectores de memoria (activación rápida)","guid":"V5f3vXWAgXhXI8W7qwXz1A","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"- Ac anti-HLA preformados (transfusiones, embarazo, trasplantes previos)","guid":"jU52_LOIYFnQmFE_3x11Jg","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"- Incompatibilidad HLA donante → estimula respuesta inmune","guid":"35hP7ZsA-8Jym-lZx4Xr-A","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"11","text":"- Poblaciones hiper-respondedoras (niños < 6 años, raza negra)","guid":"-NC0TWll1X7C84VC5lhkNQ","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"11","text":"- Inflamación (isquemia-reperfusión) → activa respuesta inmune específica","guid":"yTwXTQTZaFewubQo_ll3Fg","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"10","text":"- Objetivo\\NFundamental:","guid":"Fsj-IDPEzR_HDOelkqJwPA","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"- Eliminar/neutralizar células T reactivas (inicio)","guid":"qEZsbVKMZYW6vyd-mxZy3w","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"- Proteger injerto (efectos isquemia-reperfusión)","guid":"GdZKjdDEbfHyLW4_RXl2gg","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"- Generar tolerancia → mínima inmunosupresión de mantención","guid":"PwrFgHkc0peda_y1VrzMHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"10","text":"- Tendencia: Uso de inducción con anticuerpos ↑ (25% → 70% en trasplante renal, 1994-2003)","guid":"7XAxAd7Skk36eQ2RwJvpoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"## INDUCCIÓN CON\\NANTICUERPOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"### 1. OKT3\\N(Anti-CD3 Murino)","guid":"e4TYvHlizvZQR0nNGkmgvw","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"- Historia: Waksman (1961, ratas), Starzl (1967, humano - suero antilinfocitario), OKT3 (globulinas anti-CD3)","guid":"pZCwCsCqBr3oveGG1iyxLg","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"- Mecanismo\\Nde acción:","guid":"GAdssioVGqEpXmS2aYAmzw","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"- Une subunidad CD3 → desactiva complejo CD3/TCR → endocitosis TCR","guid":"8xvhheC1cg_SloPjRoe42Q","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"- Opsonización y remoción LT de circulación (1 hora)","guid":"rtiTJkv0PIeeSUG8bDFNBw","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"- Depleción transitoria LT (CD4, CD8, CD11) → reaparecen con CD3 débil","guid":"M24dzEVRPqTTZ-i18XZWtA","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"24","text":"- Indicaciones:","guid":"ZVuCiyEVReXv7TOpeMx-xg","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"- Inducción (hasta 80s)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"- Rechazo agudo refractario a esteroides","guid":"hWO2ieOzKZ8TI6YVbXWzAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"24","text":"- Contraindicaciones: Sensibilidad previa a proteínas OKT3","guid":"q90AfeH0wH5N64WRWBrbkA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"24","text":"- Efectos\\Nadversos:","guid":"AH_x63Wsv-g9AtxZp13uwg","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"- Síndrome de liberación de citoquinas (fiebre, calofríos, edema pulmonar, distress resp., deterioro renal transitorio, cefalea, encefalopatía) → requiere UCI, monitorización, premedicación","guid":"WSf0JPJZ5pr3_rnW_yndUg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"- Contraindicado: Plétora pulmonar, alergia, inestabilidad hemodinámica","guid":"yQkRKMR2GpX0Y0_zgnERFw","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"- Largo plazo: > incidencia infecciones oportunistas, linfomas","guid":"gv6WC-hhpMB8iYDYj4vusg","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"24","text":"- Uso actual: Escaso (desplazado por fármacos con menos efectos adversos)","guid":"6rBg_idf9GufPAgpNDoDJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"23","text":"### 2. Anticuerpos\\NAnti-Receptor IL-2 (CD25+)","guid":"WujUcdIhCwOcC8x5KJN8ng","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"- Tipos:","guid":"OrT07arbps0pMIfH2H2I6g","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"- Basiliximab (Simulect®): Quimérico (75% humano)","guid":"gc3SHgNjYSM-nU1avyBUrg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"- Daclizumab (Zenapax®): Humanizado (90% humano)","guid":"o8IbvEWLKZDa6gAdxwMKxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"- Características: Vida media > 7 días, ↓ incidencia rechazo agudo, permiten diferir inicio ACN","guid":"ouhmBAxl6OmgClsQiWiL8Q","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"39","text":"- Mecanismo de acción:","guid":"1HPl1oXunKCAuBeQwmV6Sw","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"- CD25 sobre-regulado en LT activados → estimula genes IL-2/IFNγ, activa PI-3K/JAK3 → mTOR → proliferación","guid":"KhSMTXYxV8KxwD_OB4CLMQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"- Bloquean receptor CD25 → desactivan producción citoquinas efectoras","guid":"pVxKfifVtvavNISJohZXNw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"- No provocan lisis celular / depleción linfocitaria","guid":"uFivbGHMpYAkmCc5wcolPQ","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"- Bloqueo por saturación: Basiliximab (días 0, 4 → 4-5 sem); Daclizumab (c/15 días x 3 meses)","guid":"zYmvlEzmsu9p34oihg-qxw","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"39","text":"- Indicaciones:","guid":"gNo2_xgcMzQxLHCciLqcxw","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"- Inducción (bajo/mediano riesgo inmunológico: raza blanca, no sensibilizados, poca isquemia fría)","guid":"iFtpCDwsZzM4myHY7F3x1w","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"- Mejora riesgo rechazo temprano (vs placebo)","guid":"w7iaYZlfqDx94DEh6roZjw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"- Permite diferir ACN (función retardada)","guid":"3lGyXZ1ic1wepypBBIf25w","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"49","text":"- Protocolos: eliminar esteroides precozmente, usar bajas dosis ACN","guid":"XJLqYqrBujks6wq0eQv0nQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"39","text":"- Efectos adversos: Carentes de efectos importantes, no ↑ CMV / malignidades","guid":"AgMGtyZfQVoOsp0Ijyk1uQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"23","text":"### 3. Anticuerpos\\NPoliclonales","guid":"vPc-AVkA36Kg5p1rINb0Pw","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"- Tipos:","guid":"q9u1aWruSDDNIVWZ27Xvdg","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Atgam (Linfocitos humanos → caballo)","guid":"M7PMVP8BJKJaRePLj_f_cQ","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"- Timoglobulina (TG), ATG (Timocitos humanos → conejo)","guid":"YJeEehiqdOyKtdtjZfs40Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"- Características: Gran acción lítica y apoptótica (LT, LB)","guid":"hzWktteSLYJ2N_8bjGiosA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"55","text":"- Mecanismo de acción:","guid":"EpSZ1rmr9d938cQju2QOPw","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- Bloquean proteínas membrana LT (CD2, CD3, CD45+)","guid":"g6ryXbXLEa6QkfaYN9eqNA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"- Alteraciones funcionales → apoptosis","guid":"lEgBXgTUoD-e5gK60f3mxw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"- Depleción prolongada LT (severa), moderada LB/NK; no actúan sobre granulocitos","guid":"H4s_xlwfAY3mCGuwRTYRgA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"- Unen receptores APC → modifican capacidad estimulatoria","guid":"z6HEmRZwPbAVu1QBAepqZw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"- In vitro: provocan proliferación LT reguladores","guid":"FYZHGksryE0NRgVWuf2Nzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"55","text":"- Indicaciones:","guid":"2tzWTgIku_KFmW31jxgbKQ","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"- Inducción (alto riesgo inmunológico, sospecha daño isquemia-reperfusión, postergar inicio ACN)","guid":"yYxR_74c5FY2-DCeXgz1bA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"- TG/ATG > potencia (?)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"- Uso intraoperatorio recomendado","guid":"GgID8kn9GsF2GDSCV5MyEw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"- Tratamiento rechazo resistente a esteroides","guid":"Lb684hHm92-2MxL9u5xsEQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"66","text":"- Tratamiento rechazo mediado por anticuerpos (combinado)","guid":"7i1f0NLQ3L1trgL8obTPrQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"55","text":"- Monitorización: Primeras dosis (similar OKT3), objetivo LT < 100/mm³","guid":"ZynxbKwhsEnrrUdSKc8JjQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"55","text":"- Efectos adversos:","guid":"wSWIghEKkHrnP3XpAWgb-g","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"- Síndrome liberación citoquinas (precauciones = OKT3)","guid":"QiQORbpMjlw7gnYhPHIz8g","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"- > incidencia CMV / Enf. linfo proliferativa (vs Antagonistas IL-2R)","guid":"Ez50vXUmVFaZeCT1FAc2vw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"23","text":"### 4. Alemtuzumab (Campath-1H®)\\N(Anti-CD52 Humanizado)","guid":"aDt3W4GHMEu46B4zvDhxHA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"- Características: No aprobado por FDA para trasplante","guid":"EjNRFNKd5H8uymtK9yc4Pg","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"- Antígeno CD52: Presente en LT, LB, NK, células dendríticas; Ausente en plasmocitos","guid":"MQyZjZXrDPoimtGf_fmoHg","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"- Mecanismo de acción:","guid":"7bBYpIP09D2MwR1JT1-3Vw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"- Depleción excelente poblaciones reactivas (99% sangre periférica < 1h; 3-5 días en linfonodos)","guid":"2gk-GIwa_f6oFEI0WpzUag","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"- Aumenta proporción LT reguladores → tolerancia","guid":"Locg_3TIljY29ienFHSrUw","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"- Acción débil en LT/LB de memoria (?)","guid":"phEiDVthrEbgPphUopFo0A","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"- Cobertura en Necrosis Tubular Aguda (NTA) → permite inicio retrasado ACN","guid":"axBS6csP05DfoAfydKldoQ","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"79","text":"- Requiere tto. mantención con ACN (no suprime memoria)","guid":"E79xuZH0M0X2WvDUYWA-jw","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"76","text":"- Indicaciones (Uso\\Nno universal):","guid":"0zeGREY4zEgx04tTlQZt8A","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- Receptores altamente sensibilizados","guid":"liopiul9Jan61uFt-SGoww","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- Sujetos raza negra","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"- Donantes límite (alto riesgo función retardada)","guid":"K9z_CmmOxjjfKKaZRyy1_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"76","text":"- Protocolos: Disminución significativa IS mantención (si no Ac anti-HLA donante)","guid":"AJHlLM-8A94G2CJqASCz4A","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"76","text":"- Tratamiento rechazo resistente a esteroides","guid":"7HgwK_8-AZZVg0m3k3Xu3w","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"76","text":"- Dosificación: Controversial; usual: 30 mg IV única intraoperatoria (2-4h); Ocasional: 2 dosis 30mg; Reciente: 30 mg SC","guid":"ie2gLN-nd0tnhbdpY-t7lw","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"76","text":"- Potencial: Favorece monoterapia ACN, minimización ACN, suspensión (trasplante hepático)","guid":"GRiQkkdVQN4mkjpU4nF-2Q","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"76","text":"- Efectos adversos:","guid":"ThfNm6oig_Z1Q88eCCse9g","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"- Síndrome liberación citoquinas (moderado)","guid":"tG9vWnSrfp8ajCmq2ReUqQ","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"- Pancitopenia, Trombocitopenia autoinmune","guid":"CiYlu2OjcQzBoQXZoQsMGg","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"- Enfermedad tiroidea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"93","text":"- Linfopenia persistente, Neutropenia febril","guid":"EG20qmW-b-bwXa3xzbXdcg","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"93","text":"- Incidencia similar a otros anti-T: Infecciones oportunistas (CMV, EBV), malignidades","guid":"9bLVV5JX2loRTAhyPGzj_A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"23","text":"### 5. Rituximab (Mabthera®)\\N(Anti-CD20 Quimérico)","guid":"wAelVmNMq7lPH6dh_tJKAg","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"- Características: Aprobado para Linfoma no Hodgkin B; No aprobado para trasplante órganos sólidos","guid":"erZDFUL0eUWkbLMjehLS-g","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"- Mecanismo\\Nde acción:","guid":"nPCT-8lXg-2BQ72cqmBgLg","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"- Elimina mayoría células B (CD20+)","guid":"50BgE_bTqSMkzAHSehWnfg","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"- No acción directa sobre plasmocitos (productores de Ac)","guid":"pE1NXT2UM3aaJSairZn-yw","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"- Depleción completa LB (CD20) en circulación y tejidos renales (rechazo humoral)","guid":"EeJs4YWTOm63E5CAlz-pWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"99","text":"- Indicaciones (Ensayos\\Nclínicos en trasplante):","guid":"dkA36OO5MDzLF8UBM-eHfA","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- Inducción: Receptores sensibilizados (↓ aloanticuerpos), cross-match positivo","guid":"wHfgol9MVd-9CZ2-MzjqdA","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"- Regímenes de desensibilización pre-trasplante (combinado con IVIG)","guid":"HezES954Pkzrx-RPfxHJtg","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"- Tratamiento rechazo humoral agudo y crónico","guid":"KBXOhYjeaqpE1jJWYJm88w","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"99","text":"- Efectos adversos:","guid":"1uREF4ky4zbNs_7dsQyNOg","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"- Leucoencefalopatía por JC virus (descrito en LES) → vigilar déficit motor, memoria, etc.","guid":"yHGWOqCL4tdEi1tr8-fr_A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"23","text":"### 6. Belatacept® (LEA29Y) (CTLA4-Ig\\N- Inmunoglobulina de fusión)","guid":"ywb-PcnSppxDBdVs6sjzdw","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"- Mecanismo de acción:","guid":"2FRGWbk5l4qq54ZgHEE75Q","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"- Antagoniza coestimulación (presentación antigénica)","guid":"Z-nzvTJT8At5NpKajS8czg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"- Une B7-1 (CD80) y B7-2 (CD86) en APC → compite/impide unión a CD28 en LT","guid":"FCFMUWAesb5mJTvKuPUA6g","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"- Bloqueo B7-CD28 → frena generación LT efectores, propicia LT reguladores/supresores","guid":"5mJb2E-5A0EmlMdl6nfu7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"111","text":"- Estudios (BENEFIT): Con Basiliximab,\\Nesteroides, MMF (sin ACN)","guid":"mZVa4kLQyr1JW-AVI6mvhg","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"- Resultados inmunológicos = ACN (rechazo agudo ~6%/año)","guid":"WfHx553l75dJ5LElIsdYvA","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"- Mejora significativa filtración glomerular (vs ACN) → ↓ nefropatía crónica","guid":"05fTIVbX5RqVb17i1SfcLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"111","text":"- Indicaciones (En\\Nevaluación):","guid":"f2AC3TpgELc-xOUbblPXMg","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"- Sujetos bajo riesgo inmunológico","guid":"SRa0CMjZ_9V1I8w0qgvebg","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"- Pacientes donde se puede eliminar ACN","guid":"hatKnS_JxCJ7fQB1LT5-SA","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"111","text":"- Administración: EV (10 mg/kg días 0, 4; sem 2, 4, 8, 12 → 5 mg/kg mensual)","guid":"SOgB16jRTkou1iYGGY3-HQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"111","text":"- Efectos adversos: No descritos directamente; > incidencia enfermedad linfoproliferativa","guid":"pNfe-mzb8xS4RBg1SPSbmA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"## TRATAMIENTO DE\\NMANTENCIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"### 1. ESTEROIDES\\N(Glucocorticoides - GC)","guid":"F5-v2YnpGBdlfinewWfoSA","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- Mecanismo\\Nde acción:","guid":"TLtJN8ODzm7sD1_rVlr5YA","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"- Receptores GC en mayoría células mamíferos","guid":"pMnmzceXUWYp8JRpuDLvgw","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"- En CPA: Inhiben presentación antigénica","guid":"kOB73XS2QTjLjFSsNJNdNg","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"- En linfocitos: GC une receptor → trasloca al núcleo → une GRE → inhibe promotores genes citoquinas","guid":"x0XKV9rrTvbW5Ve9-pCOyA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"- Inhiben translocación NFkB","guid":"wrMYrGxeqVmguWTUTBPWCA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"126","text":"- Producen linfopenia (movilizan LT a tej. linfático)","guid":"o7LIROxe-OCbt4ZC3Ryavg","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"126","text":"- Inhiben migración LT a sitio inflamación/injerto","guid":"D2fyCfg7XvB5Jj4yI8cj_A","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"125","text":"- Tipos/Administración:","guid":"0yrBJk0vFPy6TpOESVvO_g","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"- Metilprednisolona IV: Inducción, tratamiento rechazo agudo","guid":"FQ2BgnVfEo7FrZILjgfJuQ","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"- Prednisona oral: Terapia de mantención (prodroga → prednisolona activa)","guid":"Vyaz-l_-z9H4MYY4_QW_eA","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"125","text":"- Uso post-trasplante\\Nriñón: Controversial","guid":"DjSL4fT6JBi5gGXKhBtDcg","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"- Protocolos: No uso post-inducción, suspensión, uso indefinido","guid":"m6tE9Nzhcv3yKYVv_qNhQQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"- Suspensión: ↓ efectos adversos, ↑ rechazos (reversibles con re-terapia)","guid":"990r2emvXYNSJClalA36Eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"125","text":"- Aplicación sin/suspensión: Niños no sensibilizados, diabéticos, 3ª edad, bajo riesgo inmunológico","guid":"bvq0pMQRJC6CF0WYVSLKFQ","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"125","text":"- Metabolismo: Diferente (niños, adultos, 3ª edad); ↑ niveles con contraceptivos orales, ketoconazol","guid":"sAA9OP2GzSKwSYekGipJyQ","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"125","text":"- Efectos adversos:","guid":"77WWrF_3mgrBPyqobkgQQA","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"- Aspecto facial (Cushing), hirsutismo","guid":"UIQe-tPI7M5_jigyK7tEjw","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"- Retardo crecimiento (niños)","guid":"bgcbnsMEfkPmsomVSJ1AZQ","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"- Defecto mineralización ósea (osteoporosis, osteonecrosis, fracturas)","guid":"-Vr92gj3IU_VsbRWcb-ewQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"141","text":"- > Susceptibilidad infecciones","guid":"w7QjULYdPZa947j4lIR9Ag","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"141","text":"- Diabetes (resistencia insulina, esp. con Tacrolimus)","guid":"sknLO050aTAfficU5_N7JQ","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"141","text":"- Cataratas, Hiperlipemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"141","text":"- Requerimiento hipotensores, Ganancia peso","guid":"CD-YBMtR4u5R7GgjroKMSg","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"141","text":"- Alteraciones psíquicas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"124","text":"### 2.\\NAZATIOPRINA\\N(AZA)","guid":"jNYSqRU6xs2iFKCDkcZruA","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"- Clase: Antimetabolito (derivado 6-mercaptopurina)","guid":"9iCQmbJbyCYPsEV6xmnvcA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"- Mecanismo de acción:","guid":"iw2VrSRQvj93Q4FDBgntog","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"- Inhibe síntesis de purina → interfiere síntesis/metabolismo ARN","guid":"4OI0IjyUnIWKFJHbTGH_Fw","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"- No previene activación génica; inhibe replicación génica","guid":"OjtdGlhakRP0xKZduOscOA","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"- Inhibe activación células T y B","guid":"vp_6-28aer1sVeWzgcOYvw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"- Supresor medular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"- Eficacia no depende de conteo leucocitos/linfocitos bajo","guid":"8TNrB-FgGNyC6b6MnSYx9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"150","text":"- Interacción: Alopurinol (vía xantino oxidasa común) → no recomendable uso conjunto","guid":"JFxL2j0xDQTA_Jh0MGWeGw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"150","text":"- Farmacocinética: Absorción oral ~50%; No se dializa; No excreción renal (ajustes en IR)","guid":"EUlwezCBxvPbqr0iM8IQpQ","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"150","text":"- Indicaciones: Inmunosupresión de mantención (generalmente + esteroides + ACN)","guid":"M4qWMGqp9Bpyx6jqv75kQQ","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"150","text":"- Dosificación: 2-3 mg/kg/día (ajuste según leucocitos/plaquetas)","guid":"P9wzUlmcrvFdLOtVgij2Mg","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"150","text":"- Efectos\\Nadversos:","guid":"lGxhDF3FE1DMydcHqPD2YQ","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"- Hematológicos: Leucopenia, trombocitopenia, pancitopenia","guid":"JJkRYqk7DaX0VcFs3yzPPw","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"- Hepáticos: Alteraciones pruebas hepáticas, colestasia, hepatitis, daño hepático progresivo","guid":"Lei6_7x5Me59TsGamshbEg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"124","text":"### 3. MICOFENOLATO\\NMOFETIL (MMF) Y\\NMICOFENOLATO SÓDICO\\N(MFS)","guid":"PTAdp_jkoJRv1aokxZcDdg","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"- Clase: Prodrogas del ácido micofenólico (AMF)","guid":"X5_SyFK2CSd9DUZZVshzzg","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"- Mecanismo de\\Nacción:","guid":"jawsuJms4MuQqSFt1gZ7dA","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"- Inhibe enzima IMPDH (crítica en síntesis de novo de purinas)","guid":"yqQr4DXTXf8_bvIYW9M-Tw","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"- Efecto antiproliferativo específico en linfocitos","guid":"LPTW6B-u8iQu_UMwkBxLjw","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"- Inhiben proliferación LT y LB","guid":"uzmxnybY2Qe8sxbNKr9McA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"167","text":"- Reducen formación anticuerpos","guid":"25fXc1LH5enVDztbg5Kq5g","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"167","text":"- Reducen generación LT citotóxicos","guid":"WCuUcIrU_OLfECIiljYOYA","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"167","text":"- Suprimen maduración CPA (células dendríticas)","guid":"RK4f1usYKT6BN7VFOw_5fw","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"167","text":"- Suprimen glicosilación y expresión moléculas adhesión","guid":"fG-boaEUuSIrlmAFevjs9g","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"167","text":"- Suprimen reclutamiento linfocitos/monocitos en órgano","guid":"PcaeXj2JaFJBp5bZJXd-og","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"167","text":"- Depletan macrófagos activados de tetrahidrobiopterina → efecto antiinflamatorio","guid":"SJtKY7LYxuzETEvOPmwNAw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"167","text":"- Sinérgicos con valganciclovir (tto CMV)","guid":"MEC9mNGs6CUWEXPh6hH47g","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"167","text":"- Sinérgicos con IECA/ARAII (tto nefropatías exp.)","guid":"-Yk_ZU2wj-hVgez4Db-2eA","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"165","text":"- Comparación con AZA: ↓ incidencia rechazo; ¿mejora pronóstico injerto a largo plazo? (controversia)","guid":"uxZgmWEMg87StBWIlOOu6w","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"165","text":"- Farmacocinética:","guid":"XQaUllc1xK4uB6KMnOkIuQ","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"- Oral → hidrolización → AMF (hígado) → pico 1-2h","guid":"PzFHDjGuAIbt5T-Wejs-xg","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"- AMF inactivado (glucoronizado → AMFgl) → ciclo enterohepático → 2º pico AMFgl","guid":"qABsmbviyAqHcBdmk90XTA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"- AUC ↑ leve con IR; no se modifica en diálisis","guid":"JShWz2YaY1HER0j-T14AGQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"165","text":"- Dosificación:","guid":"d1RtNkJbvPGDRhJPcURimg","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"- Estándar (adultos): MMF 2.0 g/día; MFS 1440 mg/día (recomendada en combinación con CsA)","guid":"Y2IYHYpAqBNFPegfp3fMUA","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"- Combinación con Tacrolimus/Sirolimus/Everolimus → dosis reducir 25-50%","guid":"iat_0SmxfVflSxHiaqi8FA","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"- Retiro de CsA (en esquema con MMF/MFS+prednisona) → ↑ AUC AMF → efectos tóxicos","guid":"ycFjJrNrPwe9zMEJ3usLpQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"165","text":"- Indicaciones:","guid":"8hsS3uVGtiX7I-ZoBxEP_A","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"- Asociados a ACN (+/- esteroides)","guid":"vwvcMpiiStXeldi4VTojCw","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"- No asociados a azatioprina","guid":"gvHNokTGCf5w6VcaM94ptQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"- Sí combinados con Sirolimus/Everolimus (dosis 50% estándar)","guid":"QOVMj6WtuV_CSXW2zOHWng","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"188","text":"- Receptores > riesgo inmunológico, población pediátrica, sensibilizados","guid":"e6URncFfe04Hz8yuQFpW9Q","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"188","text":"- Intolerancia por azatioprina","guid":"t-f8g7HfvqrWvyAF__mcLQ","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"188","text":"- Intención de reducir esteroides o ACN","guid":"JB6I1-J7IdKlRbLbTw9L4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"165","text":"- Contraindicaciones: Alergia, leucopenia/plaquetopenia intratables, efectos adversos persistentes","guid":"kPvXPd5_TJtUH7zbv7FNAg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"165","text":"- Monitorización: Niveles/AUC MMF → ¿mejora eficacia/evita efectos adversos? (sugerencias débiles)","guid":"g3ZWvBRthE9wo22WPvO0NQ","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"165","text":"- Efectos adversos:","guid":"bQtqm3IKbE52ZPChs_w6ow","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"- Gastrointestinales (20%): Náuseas, meteorismo, vómitos, diarrea; Esofagitis, gastritis, hemorragia digestiva","guid":"O9Hmco8IjA9n-ZhAJrDguA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"- Hematológicos: Leucopenia, trombocitopenia, anemia","guid":"JJR2hEyMkMDaLavHV9Qxng","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"- > Infecciones oportunistas / Enf. linfoproliferativa (vs AZA)","guid":"onqnCzfESqnugxxVL3Rybw","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"197","text":"- No recomendado en gestación","guid":"MNrZtfe5cu8MiRsI9Dm3ZA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"124","text":"### 4. RAPAMICINA\\N(SIROLIMUS® - SRL) Y\\NEVEROLIMUS® (CERTICAN® -\\NEVL)","guid":"oHcrEyYSd8dz-PbFghvyjA","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"- Clase: Inhibidores de mTOR (mammalian target of rapamycin)","guid":"5zhLk6GovyBCjL0phkkcnw","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"- Mecanismo\\Nde acción:","guid":"CujMehkTK6Cj2sreTW7_Ug","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"- mTOR = kinasa clave en división/proliferación celular","guid":"kK2oShnUFcOaJwBqowGUdQ","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"- Macrólido (similar a Tacrolimus) une ligando citoplasmático FKBP","guid":"VnMNbJfFuLOdrM95HVTHxA","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"- Complejo Rapamicina/FKBP/mTOR → inhibe mTOR → detiene división celular (fase G1-S)","guid":"yweCx3xr2WzI6-QM9s4_yg","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"- Afecta células hematopoyéticas y no hematopoyéticas","guid":"CZe4dt0JjvTLRsTpzgCnkA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"204","text":"- No compiten con Tacrolimus (a pesar de mismo ligando FKBP)","guid":"Bc6VKEVk7IQ-1kmyfCYd1Q","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"204","text":"- No afectan negativamente LT reguladores (vs ACN)","guid":"KDKBic3-SKf2vm4C72DP8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"- Indicaciones:","guid":"lPCHhxbOrsCpniozVixeAg","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"- Como droga de inicio (combinada con esteroides/ACN)","guid":"4020JHQ04-IiAIlMFpEW0w","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"- Uso más común: \"Conversión\" después 1º o 3º mes → reducir dosis/efectos adversos","guid":"18NeuvWXKtDBGdqI_V1dSw","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"- Conversión → minimización (50/25% dosis) o eliminación ACN","guid":"6F_9C__ABYAIYDEmSUFivQ","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"- Resultados: Mejoría FG; Leve ↑ incidencia rechazo; Ocasional ↑ proteinuria","guid":"NFasaoi-2TLsoRMBqqNXLw","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"211","text":"- Indicado convertir en: Nefrotoxicidad por ACN, Nefropatía crónica del injerto, Cáncer","guid":"H22TCbt4zsIJVSQl1DowzQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"202","text":"- Farmacocinética/Dosificación:","guid":"HgsKoditm8q84bMkgRBj6g","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"- SRL: Cápsulas 1/2 mg; Carga 6-12 mg → Mantención 2-6 mg/día; Nivel valle 6-10 ng/dl; Vida media ~60h","guid":"kkNAbuic_w6rJKZdFtMXPw","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"- EVL: Comprimidos 0.25/0.50/0.75/1.0 mg; Sin carga; Inicio 0.75 mg c/12h x 5 días → ajustar dosis","guid":"cvpaicg4kMkgaPHMOgCA-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"202","text":"- Interacciones: CsA ↑ niveles EVL; Tc no afecta niveles EVL","guid":"mU2bl86JTOTykeXptdEh3A","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"202","text":"- Ajustes: Disfunción hepática (SRL); No ajuste por disfunción renal","guid":"XxJ2r9ImaoVzq9oOezRHUg","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"202","text":"- Efectos\\Nadversos:","guid":"SCFBEos8uBJPTymSkt3YSg","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"- Cutáneos: Rash, acné","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"- Mucosas: Úlceras bucales","guid":"mMtUt3R69CLFRF1R17YvkA","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"- Generales: Edema, alteraciones GI","guid":"zMpdPOtAvqT5zFycLxzElg","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"- Hematológicos: Anemia, leucopenia, trombocitopenia","guid":"2IG47U8N_GjVSZZOwL3meg","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"222","text":"- Renales: Proteinuria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"222","text":"- Metabólicos: Hiperlipemia (controlable)","guid":"xBpREsy8LvfcpJKGkgtXew","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"222","text":"- Quirúrgicos: > incidencia linfocele, retardo cicatrización","guid":"VfGIN2C5PyAyMTIyM-8euw","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"222","text":"- Nefrotoxicidad potenciada con ACN (CsA > Tc)","guid":"KJ_l_4eajTWpGiJeWS6BCQ","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"222","text":"- Pulmonares: Neumonías severas (desaparecen al suspender)","guid":"DdfB947BJWoMc7LxMVYhhg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"124","text":"### 5. ANTICALCINEURÍNICOS (ACN):\\NCICLOSPORINA (CSA) Y TACROLIMUS (TC)","guid":"DsLDRbAdAS0MW1PGaN7wUA","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"- Clase: Principales inmunosupresores en trasplante órganos sólidos/médula","guid":"UAxjtxLbi8XNCH7dkD1TAQ","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"232","text":"- Mecanismo\\Nde acción:","guid":"jKQhgeJa-Vx5rhwlVv0Obg","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"- Actúan principalmente en LT y LB; también en CPA","guid":"cKQ3dZg1vwwu-oxXWBpVsQ","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"- Unen ligandos citosólicos: CsA → Ciclofilina; Tc → FKBP","guid":"57lLj39kzN4MzbxzeyoE6w","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"234","text":"- Complejo droga/ligando → inhibe Calcineurina (fosfatasa)","guid":"qrNKHPEtU7rRuGdm_GYxkg","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"234","text":"- Calcineurina inhibida → no defosforila proteínas reguladoras → no ingresan al núcleo","guid":"nOWbRico_Jo0BCuRMjaLug","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"234","text":"- Resultado: Inhibición genes de citoquinas pro-rechazo","guid":"l6EStgOQ--2fDtd2uqXB7g","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"234","text":"- CsA ↑ expresión TGFβ (antagonista efectores rechazo)","guid":"28Nq3tTC5W6_0IH_fJNnkg","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"234","text":"- Acción dependiente de concentración (disipa al disminuir nivel) → versatilidad","guid":"iYDdxvLXZIpj7qtcpzQ9qw","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"232","text":"- Indicaciones: Medicamentos electivos en todo trasplante (mayor eficacia IS)","guid":"0DxoXiAjPzyScZDw5B0qVQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"232","text":"- Contraindicaciones relativas: Intolerancia, nefrotoxicidad severa, diabetes post-trasplante, neurotoxicidad","guid":"AHaIUxqPG-RN6NrZlCVFuw","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"232","text":"- Efectos adversos\\Ncomunes / Nefrotoxicidad:","guid":"uGvYcHoWsC66talvoj4GXg","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"- Funcionales: ↓ FG (vasoconstricción aferente), retención Na+, edema, HTA, hiperK, hipoMg","guid":"DWzpaEr6BL6A749TY7iamQ","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"- Estructurales: Microvacuolización túbulos, necrosis tubular, fibrosis intersticial, esclerosis glomerular","guid":"o4en_fS8z8M2pdgcfJl-Kw","children":[]}]},{"id":"247","parent":"232","text":"#### 5.1\\NCICLOSPORINA (CSA -\\NNeoral®)","guid":"ud49HZncGBhIK9XY088AqQ","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"- Formulación: Emulsionada","guid":"_PxtpsNmn97aJl7edVumwA","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"247","text":"- Farmacocinética: Absorción intestinal, Cmax 1-3h, T1/2 12-16h, BD ~40%, alimentos ↑ absorción","guid":"fTdIVBiZh3IO-etLQnXiBQ","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"247","text":"- Dosificación: Inicio 6-8 mg/kg/día (c/12h); Mantención 2-3 mg/kg/día","guid":"Wys2vUnQwj15_xZtCgDWrA","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"247","text":"- Monitorización (sangre total): Niveles C0 (valle) / C2 (pico)","guid":"Akoaj6FNBB1dzZLghwtVtQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"247","text":"- Efectos adversos específicos: Hirsutismo, hipertrofia gingival, alopecia (más que Tc)","guid":"7MoxqtYxACwjPQQgaAT4tA","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"247","text":"- Interacciones farmacológicas: Muchas (inductores/inhibidores CYP450)","guid":"7yZy0Go5c0sMmkyIj7nuQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"232","text":"#### 5.2 TACROLIMUS\\N(TC - Prograf®)","guid":"oY2x_pFGXiric84qKnaTsA","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"- Clase: Macrólido (Streptomyces tsukubaensis)","guid":"Z56hsvVKxCY5SRGeKKkJZw","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"- Potencia: ~100 veces > CsA (a = concentración)","guid":"HXEike3MWYRm4aAQgM6ZWA","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"254","text":"- Mecanismo: Similar CsA, une FKBP","guid":"nIXPW55vXz5I52nAp7wmZg","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"254","text":"- Eficacia: > inhibición incidencia rechazo post-trasplante (vs CsA)","guid":"QcyPzp_slzHRtkbDhCEMnQ","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"254","text":"- Indicaciones:","guid":"dDMZWdXs7KD8NSVSajDunA","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"- Alternativa a Neoral® (elección según protocolo local)","guid":"XZamjaZQPx4ssNHeDYd5Kg","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"- Generalizado en trasplante pediátrico (evita efectos cosméticos CsA)","guid":"WSXWCvYk1p1tGoRBRH2TLA","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"259","text":"- Trasplantes con > riesgo inmunológico","guid":"ebd9OeUBF0iJ5gh5uOhqwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"263","parent":"254","text":"- Resultados largo plazo (renal): Similares a CsA","guid":"ZWNpWbhi33Apdby5izMHNQ","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"254","text":"- Efectos adversos específicos: Neurotoxicidad, Intolerancia glucosa / Diabetes (más que CsA)","guid":"0rScD3xdPimXd2BDnFxSIQ","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"254","text":"- Nefrotoxicidad: Similar a CsA (paradoja: cambio a Tc puede aliviar nefrotoxicidad CsA y viceversa)","guid":"iLAmanva7GQfNlW8dA6y7w","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":265,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Bioestadística","filename":"Paper. DROGAS INMUNOSUPRESORAS-2025-1","id":"map_195","resolved_references":[]}